  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.foreach.across.modules.hibernate.business.Auditable<String>, com.foreach.across.modules.hibernate.business.EntityWithDto<T>, com.foreach.across.modules.hibernate.business.IdBasedEntity, WebCmsDomainBound, WebCmsChildComponentRestrictable, WebCmsObject, org.springframework.data.domain.Persistable<Long>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    WebCmsAssetType, WebCmsComponentType

    @NotThreadSafe
 @Entity
public abstract class WebCmsTypeSpecifier<T extends WebCmsTypeSpecifier<T>>
extends WebCmsObjectInheritanceSuperClass<T>
implements WebCmsChildComponentRestrictable
    Represents a sub-type specifier for a particular asset or component. This serves as a base class. Every sub-type has a unique id, a type and key that is expected to be unique within the type. A sub-type also has a more descriptive name that is also expected to be unique within the type.
    Since:
    0.0.1
    Author:
    Arne Vandamme
